name: asuitthatfits
overview: A Suit That Fits Ltd. provides tailoring services in the United Kingdom. It designs and tailors shirts, morning coats, and dinner suits. The company was founded in 2006 and is based in London, United Kingdom. It has branches in Aberdeen, Birmingham, Bury St. Edmunds, Brighton, Bristol, Cambridge, Cardiff, Chichester, Edinburgh, Exeter, Glasgow, Guildford, Leeds, Leicester, Liverpool, Manchester, Milton Keynes, Newcastle, Norwich, Nottingham, Oxford, Peterborough, Reading, Sheffield, Southampton, St Albans, and Tunbridge Wells.
